summary: Tony: Peter, let me tell you about the birds and the bees.Peter: Please...no.Tony: Did you know there are over 10,000 species of...
body:
Tony: Peter, let me tell you about the birds and the bees.

Peter: Please…no.

Tony: Did you know there are over 10,000 species of birds?

Peter: Mr. Stark-

Tony: And that bees are dying at an alarming rate?

Peter:…

Tony: Get your suit, Pete. We’re gonna save some bees.
